  "title": "Accountant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a meticulous and proactive Accounts Assistant which is responsible for a range of accounting tasks, including accounts payable (AP), accounts receivable (AR). You will assist in the preparation of full sets of management accounts, unaudited financial statements, consolidated financial statements, and business activity reports. Your contributions will also include financial accounting, corporate reporting activities, preparation and submission of Quarterly GST Return</p>\n<p>- Min Diploma in Accounting</p>\n<p>- Responsible for invoicing / partial accounts</p>\n<p>- Experience in Shipping Industries will be considered advantage</p>\n<p>- Committed, meticulous and hardworking</p>\n<p>- Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable processes.<br>\n- Prepare and submit GST returns and tax computations.</p>\n<p>- Prepare Monthly closing report</p>\n<p>- Preparation of audit schedule</p>\n<p>- Preparation of Monthly AR and AP Overdue Reports</p>",
